channel.title: Blank Source and Client
channel.description:
I'm looking for a blank 317 source and client.
I've been looking for hours, on moparscape and on google (I found one on moparscape but it's a horrible half leeched czar one). But sadly I couldn't find anything.
I don't care what it is based one, do prefer delta tho.
Does anybody maybe know where I could get one?
Thanks.

Thanks, but I’m not looking for a completely blank server with only a few things. I’m actually kinda looking for a cleaned server, all NPC’s removed and Shops etc.

Edit:

Nvm, I found out I was looking for blank, but actually had to look for clean :P. Found a perfect one. Can be closed.
